## Verification checklist

- Contracts route to PRD 09 only.
- Street Deals and debts route to PRD 10 only.
- Contacts route to PRD 11 only.
- Turf Levels route to PRD 12 only.
- Accepted `FIX-*` decisions are followed exactly.
- No duplicated runtime ownership was introduced.
- AI received no contracts, contacts, or Street Deal choices.
- Human-only choices remain human-only.
- Deterministic offers and random side effects use unified random.
- Contract claim/deadline rules are mutation-safe.
- Debts process through Income owner flow.
- Contact limit is max 1 with no replacement.
- Turf effects are cumulative and Turf Level cannot change during a match.
